tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE FarmingEquipmentInventory (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    item_name VARCHAR(255),
    quantity INT,
    price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    category VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE farming_equipment (
  equipment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  equipment_name VARCHAR(255),
  equipment_type VARCHAR(255),
  quantity INT,
  price DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE farm_equipment (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name TEXT NOT NULL,
    type TEXT NOT NULL,
    quantity INT NOT NULL,
    price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE farm_machinery (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name TEXT NOT NULL,
    type TEXT NOT NULL,
    quantity INT NOT NULL,
    price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    maintenance_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE farm_tractors (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    brand TEXT NOT NULL,
    model TEXT NOT NULL,
    horse_power INT NOT NULL,
    fuel_type TEXT NOT NULL,
    price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE farm_harvesters (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    brand TEXT NOT NULL,
    model TEXT NOT NULL,
    cutting_width INT NOT NULL,
    price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    production_year YEAR
);

CREATE TABLE farm_accessories (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name TEXT NOT NULL,
    category TEXT NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL
);
